title: BBC R4 - Justin Butcher's 'The Seven White Masks Of Scaram
description:
BBC R4 - Justin Butcher's 'The Seven White Masks Of Scaramouche Jones'
Directed by Claire Grove
Broadcast March 9, 2001
Coded from tape at 128/44.1

Warren Mitchell plays Scaramouche Jones, a white faced clown.

Scaramouche is 100 years old. On the last night of his life
he tells the tale of his seven masks and his strange destiny.
It is a journey through the dark heart of the 20th century.
